0%5Cnotin%7BA%7D\" alt=\"p:\\exists{n_0}\\in\\mathbb{N}_+,2n_0\\notin{A}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e逆否命题的后键 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=q%3A-1%E6%98%AF%E8%B4%A8%E6%95%B0\" alt=\"q:-1是质数\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e要证明逆否命题成立，也就是证明 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=p%5Crightarrow+q\" alt=\"p\\rightarrow q\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果是为了证明前件\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=p\" alt=\"p\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e，那么找一个特例，比如 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=n_0%3D1\" alt=\"n_0=1\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ，就能证明了。但是现在 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=p\" alt=\"p\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 是一个“假设为真”的条件，要证明的是 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=q\" alt=\"q\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ，这时对 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=p\" alt=\"p\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 找特例没有意义。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e用特例证明时，相当于换了一个前件\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ep': 2∈A\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然后仅仅证明了 p'→q\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e同时，因为 p 只需要一个特例即可证明，显然有  p'→p\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是，并没有 p→p' ，所以光从 p 是证明不出 q 的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"原证明的关键错误就在于，哥德巴赫猜想变式一的逆否命题“若\\exists{n_0}\\in\\mathbb{N}_+,2n_0\\notin{A}，则-1不是质数。”不能用一个特例来证明。逆否命题的前件 p:\\exists{n_0}\\in\\mathbb{N}_+,2n_0\\notin{A} 逆否命题的后键 q:-1是质数 要证明逆否命题成…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"vo